    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Lets say you want to assign the third value in newarray to the third index in result.\nThat would be like:</p>\n\n<pre><code>result[2] = newarray[2]\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 284109,
      "reputation" : 47819,
      "user_id" : 581994,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 57,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/d2ae9ac6fb51918297a0ce5dada0eb22?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
